See, I considered that and gave it a shot, but all it resulted in was having my visa application sent back to me letting me know I missed a field. So I filled in &quot;other&quot; and wrote &quot;Iberian&quot; in the little line provided. When I received my approval, I notice &quot;white&quot; was shaded in.<br>
